Name: CodeListReference
Description: A reference to the CodeList included in this representation using the Reference structure.

Name: StatisticalClassificationReference
Description: A reference to the StatisticalClassification included in this representation using the Reference structure.

Name: CodeSubsetInformation
Description: Allows further specification of the codes to use from the CodeList by defining the level or only the most discrete codes of a hierarchical CodeList, the range of codes to use, or an itemized sub-set.
